title: Draft (Vi)kings | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
It’s Week 9 and we’re going all in on the Minnesota Vikings against the Chiefs, plus an appreciation for Josh Jacobs, and our weekly “Is Melvin Gordon good?” discussion (1:45). Then, we introduced a new segment called Galaxy Brain, discover the bargain buy of the year on the Eagles, and build our daily fantasy lineup for the weekend (28:00).
Hosts: Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck
